---
title: Chicken and Chorizo Stew with Cannelini Beans and Spinach
description: It’s hard to beat the simple pleasure of a comforting stew. Seasoned with herbs and packed with hearty cannellini beans and fresh spinach, our chicken and chorizo stew is bowl food at its best. Quick and simple to prep, serve everything up in deep bowls along with fresh garlic ciabatta perfect for dunking.
